title: Wall Street Breakfast: The Week Ahead
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Big bank earnings expected to drop significantly following Russia’s invasion of Ukraine. Spotlight on retail crime and how some of the biggest U.S. chains are affected. Elon Musk takes on social media, as he becomes Twitter’s largest stakeholder, and Tesla ramps up production.
